    "implementing_authority": "state",
    "methodology_vintage": "NITI Aayog ICED state-wise deep-dive API; payload fetched 2026-05-14T07:51:49Z; 10 fiscal years, 344 rows.",
    "notes": "Source: NITI Aayog ICED dashboard, row 'AT&C Losses'. Calculated by PFC. The Government's UDAY targets envisaged AT&C losses below 15% all-India by 2018-19; the actual all-India figure has hovered around 15% since then."
